==Definition==

<b>Humor</b> (<i>noun</i>)
# Something [[funny]] such as a [[joke]], [[satire]], [[parody]], etc...
# (<i>archaic</i>) (plural <b>humors</b>) Four "fluids" that were believed to control the health and mood of the human body.
:M. Le Page Du Pratz, <i>History of Louisisana</i> (PG), p. 40
:: <i>For some days a </i>fistula lacrymalis<i> had come into my left eye, which discharged an <b>humour</b>, when pressed, that portended danger.</i>

